Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
I was recently invited to a relative's wedding... The wedding dress was beautiful...
I'm sure that the dress would look good on ▲高嶺＊＊▲, too.
Eh？ Me！？ I-I wonder... Thanks. I actually caught the bouquet.
I see. Then ▲高嶺＊＊▲ will be wearing it sooner or later.
Geez... Can you not say such things so lightly？
By the way, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. You don't get sunburn, right？ Even though you practice outside all the time...
Manaka
Yeah. It's probably genetics... I'm thinking about using sunscreen. Will my skin get tanned evenly？
S-Sunscreen！？
What's wrong？
Nothing... Hahaha.
...Why are you smirking？ Are you imagining something indecent？
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Are you lonely？
Manaka
Eh...？ No, I'm not lonely because you're with me.
I see. From now on, I won't let you feel lonely.
O-Okay... Thank you...
Manaka
By the way, there was power outage last night. It was dark and scary...
I never knew ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is afraid of the dark.
Yeah, a little bit... Eh？ Your face is red... Do you have a cold？
It must be because of that dream...
Dream...？ Anyway, let me check whether you have a fever.
A fever！？ I'm okay！ No problem！
...Really？ Then that's fine...
Hey, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Can you show me your childhood photos？
Manaka
...Why？
I just want to see them...
...No, it's embarrassing.
(That's too bad...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you and I didn't know each other when we were little, right？
Manaka
Eh！？ We didn't know each other, not until high school. Have you forgotten？
Yeah... you're right, that's right.
...Weirdo.
(Hmm, I believe I saw the dream in that manner...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, have you read "Romeo and Juliet"？
Manaka
Of course. If Romeo were a little more reliable, the two could've lived their lives happily...
Right. A man has to protect the person he loves with his life！
Yeah, a man like that must be wonderful...
Manaka
By the way, there was the international championship for the doubles tennis match.
Japan team did their best. Now I feel so pumped up.
Of course, ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s smash was wonderful. That "Air MANA"！
...What are you talking about？
Sorry. It was nothing. Hahaha...
Manaka
I plan to cook some sweet potatoes. Do you want to try some？
Sweet potatoes...？ That sounds yummy, but make sure you don't eat too much.
Hey, I'm not that much of a glutton！
Haha, sorry, sorry.
Hey, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Between sumo and food, which one do you like better？
Manaka
Eh？ Well... Why did you bring up those two choices together？
Just a little curious.
Hmm...？ Then... Food.
(Yeah, I knew you'd say that！)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Ah！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
What's wrong？ You're all fidgety.
Ah, that's... Well... You see...
Hehe. Here you go.
I've been waiting！
Hey, just take it already.
Thank you！ Can I really open it？
No, it's too embarrassing. Open it later.
Eh？ Okay...
Hm, very well. Yeah... Just enjoy it at home, okay？
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. Hey, come here for a moment.
Huh？ What is it？
...Well. Here's your chocolate.
I see. It's Valentine's！
Yeah. Will you accept it？
Of course！ Yeah！ Thanks, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
No. Seeing you happy like this makes me happy too.
I'm glad I tried my best... Hehe.
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Ah！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ What's up？
I'm waiting to see your jaw drop.
...It's February 14th！
Hehe, of course. Here's your gift.
Yes！ Thanks！
You're welcome. Try to savor it, okay？
Okay！
Manaka
...You got a minute？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what's up？
...Here you are.
Thanks... Eh？ Is this chocolate？
I just made too many. That's it.
Even though you wrapped it neatly like this, huh？
...You don't want it？
No！ I want it！
... That's all. Bye.
(I received Valentine's chocolate from ▲高嶺＊＊▲！)
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you have a moment？
Manaka
Hmm？ What？
Nothing！ Well, do you have any business with me？
Yeah. Here. It's a gift to thank you for Valentine's.
Hehe. Thanks. Wow... Wonderful！
(She's extremely happy with it.)
Thank you. Hehe. I'm happy.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...Thanks.
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Sort of...
Hehe. You really tried hard for me. Thanks. I'll treasure it.
Hearing you say that makes this really worth the effort of picking it out.
Hehe. I guess this kind of conversation is very common among couples all around the world...
I guess so.
I'm glad that we're one of those couples. Let's get along well later on too, okay？
Agreed！
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Got a moment？
Manaka
Ah... Y-Yeah. What is it？
Here. Today's White Day, isn't it？ This is to thank you for Valentine's.
...Okay. Actually, I've been waiting... I'm kidding.
Haha！ Is that so？ You can open it now.
Wow... I'm so happy！ Thank you. I'll treasure it.
(She's extremely happy with it.)
Thanks. You really know what I like...
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...Thanks. I guess I can use this somehow...
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Did it take you a while to pick this？
Yeah, but I had a nice time choosing it.
Yeah, time flies fast when you imagine the smiling face of the person who'll receive your gift, right？
That's right. So, don't worry about me.
Okay.
...Hehe.
Hmm？ What？
I just received another treasure. I'm happy.
(She's extremely happy like this. It was worth the effort picking this for her.)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. You got a moment？
Manaka
Of course, yes.
Eh？ You are making that face...
It's March 14th, right？ I'm tired of waiting！ I'm kidding.
Haha. I see. Sorry to keep you waiting. Here you go.
How did you know what I like？ Hehe. Thanks！
(She's extremely happy with it.)
Your sense is quite nice. Thanks.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...Thanks. I'll have to figure out how I can use this...
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
I don't feel comfortable receiving this.
But it's a return gift, you know？
...Did you go around giving gifts to other girls, too？
O-Of course not！ How could that be！？
Haha, just kidding. Let's do this again next year.
Roger that.
Hehe, very well. Next year and the years after too, okay？
Hahaha. Okay.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. You got a moment？
Manaka
Ah...
Eh？
Nothing！ What is it？
Ah, yes. Here's a return gift for Valentine's.
Hehe. Wonderful. I'm happy. Thanks.
(She's extremely happy with it.)
Thank you so much. I like it.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
Well... Um, thanks...
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Hey, as a guy, how did you feel when you bought this？
Why？
I guess most guys don't like to enter this kind of shop.
Yeah, that's true. But when I thought of your smiling face when you received it, I didn't mind being in such a store.
Hmm... Then you pictured my smiling face when you chose this, huh？
Yeah, something like that.
Really？ ...Then can I have some expectations for this gift...？
Nothing. Thanks. I'll treasure it.
(What were you trying to say, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Manaka
...What's wrong？ You don't look too well.
It's nothing.... Yeah...
It's nothing？
Y-Yeah...
Really？ That's fine then. ...Idiot.
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Manaka
What's wrong？ You've been staring at me. Is there anything you want？
No, I didn't want anything. Rather, I didn't have anything for you...
You didn't have anything for me...？ I see. Then I'm leaving now.
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Manaka
Hey, do you know what day it is today？
Today is... March 14th...
...Could it be that you forgot？
Um, well...
...I don't care anymore！
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Manaka
...Do you need me for something？ You don't look too well.
No, it's nothing...
...Hmph... Idiot.
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(All right. Today is the sports festival.)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. It's finally arrived...
Manaka
Good morning. How's your physical condition？
Not bad, I guess.
I see. That's good. I'll be cheering for you since we're on the same team. Do your best.
Hahaha, leave it to me！
Hehe. Don't get too enthusiastic and hurt yourself. Don't forget to stretch too, okay？
Yeah, I'll be careful. Thanks.
Well then, I'll see you later.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ is cheering for me. I'll do my best.)
(All right, perfect！)
Manaka
That was a big win！ That surprised me.
Thanks. It was surely because ▲高嶺＊＊▲ was cheering for me.
Eh？ You could hear my voice？
Hehe, I guess I was able to help a bit. If so, I'm happy.
(This is thanks to me for training regularly...)
(It was no good at all...)
Manaka
That's too bad...
I guess I was a bit short on practice... Sorry, since you were even cheering for me.
Don't worry. I think it's good to just go all out... Most importantly, you did your best, and that's wonderful.
Thanks, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
(I'll have to train some more...)
(Well, today is the culture festival.)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. I just heard that you joined the Most Handsome Man Contest. Is it true？
Ah, yeah. It's true. My friends just put my name in it without me knowing...
Hmm...
W-What？ Don't stare at me like that？
Sorry. I'm just thinking that you got such good qualities for it.
R-Really？
You need to get the right angle. Turn a bit to the right... That's what I love most... I'm kidding.
Eh？ L-Love！？
！！ I didn't mean it that way. I meant you look calm like that. Yeah, so don't get the wrong idea！
Is that so？ Hahaha.
...Hey.
(My heart skipped a beat for a moment.)
(I won the contest...)
Manaka
You really won. That's wonderful.
No, it's nothing.
...If you become popular after this, what should I do？
Eh？
Nothing！ Anyway, congratulations.
(It's good that I always take care of my appearance.)
(The contest result was totally no good...)
Manaka
It was a bit unfortunate...
Yeah. I guess I'm not suited to be the most handsome man.
No, that's not it！ For me, you are the most... Ah！
Huh？
Nothing！ Anyway, you did a great job there.
(I should've paid more attention to my appearance.)
Hmm, I'm getting so excited...
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Merry Christmas.
Hehe, Merry Christmas.
Wow, you look good in this dress...
I thought it was just a normal dress, but thank you. By the way, it's so crowded here.
Right. It would be better if we could be alone, just the two of us.
Hey, don't say it out loud like that... But I feel the same way...
I got a present for you.
Oh, thank you！ I got something for you, too.
Then let's exchange them.
Okay...
Wonderful... You got such nice sense. Thank you. I'll treasure it.
(She's extremely happy with it.)
Hehe, so cute. Thanks.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
Hey, this thing... No, never mind. Thanks.
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Um, about presents...
Hmm？ Presents？ Are you talking about Santa Claus？
Eh？ Ah, no. Never mind.
(Geez. I should've gotten something for her.)
Hey, will you... come with me for a moment？
Hmm？
Well, it's time to go home.
I see. Bye.
Hmm, I'm getting so excited...
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Merry Christmas. Are you enjoying yourself？
Merry Christmas.
▲高嶺＊＊▲... You look good in that dress.
Really？ Thank you. I'm really glad you came. I've been looking for you.
Hm？ Do you need me for something？
No. But at a time like this, I feel like I want to be with you... Somewhat...
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ is just so cute...)
By the way, I got you a present.
Oh, thank you！ I have something for you, too.
Then let's exchange them.
Okey...
You're like a wizard... Thank you. I'll treasure it.
(She's extremely happy with it.)
I like it. Thank you very much.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...Thanks. Hey, is this thing very trendy？
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
By the way, you know about presents...
Haha, presents？ I don't think Santa Claus will give me anything this year.
Ah, then... I see...
(Geez. I should've gotten something for her.)
Hey, I have a place I want us to go to. Can you？
Hmm？
It's time to go home. It's quite late already.
I see. Bye.
Hmm, I'm getting so excited...
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. Merry Christmas.
Merry Christmas. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, your dress really suits you.
Hehe, thanks.
But with this big crowd, how did you know that I was here？
I'm quite confident that I can find you wherever you are. Isn't it the same for you？
I... I don't think so.
You get dizzy with so many people, huh？ Hehe！
Ah, right. A Christmas present.
Oh, thanks. I got something for you too.
Then let's exchange them.
Ah...
Wow！ Wonderful. Thanks. I'll treasure it.
(She's extremely happy with it.)
Um, it's nice. Thanks.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
Well... Thanks. I'll try to like it, okay？
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Hey, how about a present？
Well... Will Santa visit ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s house？ I wonder... Haha.
...Geez. I don't care now.
(Urgh. I should've gotten something for her.)
Can you come with me after this？ There's a place that I want us to go.
Hmm？
It's time to go home. It's late now.
I see. Bye.
Hmm, I'm getting so excited...
Ah, Merry Christmas, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. Merry Christmas.
It's nice to have a party like this occasionally.
Yeah. Hmm？ Such a nice gown, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. It matches you well.
Really？ I don't think it's such a big deal.
No, you really look nice. Like, even nicer than usual, and...
E-Enough about the dress.
Then... Hey... They've got some nice food there. Shall we go take some？
(...Was she getting shy？)
Manaka
The Christmas tree is twinkling...
This normal tree looks totally different when it's lit up.
Yeah. The tree must feel so warm with this many lights.
Hahaha, I guess so. Are you cold, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I'm fine. I'm very strong against cold weather, you know？
Really？？
...Are you cold？
Me？
Yup.
I'm... Kind of...
Aren't you cold？
...Huh？
You're cold, right？ Then come here. I'll warm your hands up.
...Okay.
Hehe, warm, isn't it？
Can we stay like this？ I'm so happy...
(Yeah. We come close and hold hands... But I guess that's it...)
Ah, the tree was lit.
Manaka
It's beautiful...
Yeah. It really feels like Christmas.
Hehe, I agree. We can see this only during this season.
It's quite cold, though... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you okay？
Well, I got a request... Will you hear me out？
Hm？ What is it？
Um... Can you lend me your pocket？
My pocket？ Well, fine...
...And, your hand...
Hand？ Ah...
...Um, here you go. You can do whatever you want with them.
Hehe, don't mind if I do. ...It's so warm.
Hey, can we go home a little late？ I still want to be with you...
Yeah, I want to be with you longer too. Let's walk home slowly.
(Walking hand in hand like this makes this my happiest Christmas already...)
Manaka
Wow, so pretty...！
Hahaha, your eyes are sparkling. You want to get closer？
Yeah！
...Ah, hey. Can you see what's on the top of the tree？
Yeah, I can see it.
And can you grab that star for me？
Oh, leave it to me... Geez, that's impossible！
Hehe, I was just joking！
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ is in such high spirits. She's like a little kid now.)
Hah... This is fun.
Yeah, I'm having a great time too.
And I'm very happy that I can spend Christmas Eve with the person I love. This is like a scene from a movie, don't you think？
Anyway, I feel like this is not enough.
Not enough？
Yeah, both of my hands are free now, you know？
And my hands are available, you know？
...Hey, can you also lend me your arm？
As you wish, my princess.
Hehe. Hey, how about we take a detour a little bit on our way home？
(Just being together like this makes me feel very happy...)
Urgh... So cold. Is she here yet？
Manaka
Happy New Year.
Happy New Year, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Please be nice to me this year too.
Yeah, please be nice to me too.
You're wearing a kimono. It suits you well.
Hehe. Thanks.
So, shall we go visit the shrine？
As expected. It's so crowded on New Year's.
Manaka
Give me your hand.
Eh？ My hand？ Why？
...I'll hold your hand so you won't get lost.
If you don't hurry, I'm going to leave you here.
Ah. Ah...！ Umm, please take care of me.
Um, very well！ Yeah.
What shall I wish for this year？
Manaka
You can't decide？
Yeah... I can't choose... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, have you decided on yours？
I want to live happily with someone very special to me, forever and ever.
Specifically, Papa and Mama！
Eh！？ I'm not included！？
Well, maybe you are？ Ah, that space is open. Shall we go？
(Urgh... Now I'm so concerned...)
Manaka
Thanks for walking me home. See you later.
Yeah, see you.
Hmm？
Please also be nice to me from now on.
Of course. Likewise. See you.
It's really hot tonight...
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry for the wait.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. You look good in a yukata.
Hehe, thanks.
Then shall we go to the shrine？
Manaka
Ah, candied apples！ They have oranges too！
Fine, Daddy will buy some for you.
Then, a chocolate-covered banana and some candied apricot too！
...Are you serious？
Hehe, hurry！
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ is in such a good mood.)
Manaka
Why is food from street stalls so delicious？
It's the same with curry during the school camping trips.
Yeah. But we've already bought a lot. It's dangerous... I need to be careful about overeating today.
▲高嶺＊＊▲！ Look at that buttered potato. Ah, they also have grilled squid... And cotton candy, too！
Geez, stop teasing me！
Manaka
Ah, the fireworks just now...
They were heart-shaped.
Hmm？
Nothing. I wonder if they will shoot some more...
Manaka
It's so crowded.
Seems so... Oh, over there. It looks open. Let's go.
Okay.
No wonder there's no one here...
Yeah. I didn't think that we wouldn't be able to see anything from here...
What now？ Should we head back？
Hmm... ▲高嶺＊＊▲. How about we stay for a while？ The night view is so beautiful.
...Actually, I was thinking the same thing. And I want to be with you longer.
Okay. Then how about we play with fireworks here, just the two of us？
That's good. I want to play with the sparkler.
Manaka
The fireworks are beautiful...
Are you listening？ What？ What are you staring at？
▲高嶺＊＊▲ watching the fireworks is just so beautiful.
...Hey.
Um, at times like this, I feel like we don't have to say a word to understand each other... I'm happy.
But I want to talk about fireworks with you later, so you have to watch properly, okay？
You mean watching ▲高嶺＊＊▲ or the fireworks？
...Geez...
Oh, they have that shooting game too.
Manaka
I kind of want to try it.
You've never tried it before？
...I have. I used to be very good when I was in grade school. I can aim for something on that shelf. Let's see.
Okay, okay. Then, that one！ Let's see who wins！
...Um, that rugby ball is probably a good target for a novice！
...The gun here is different from the one I used to use in grade school. And I don't like any of the prizes here.
Ah... Oh, I get it. Hahaha！
...Urgh.
(She looks somewhat disappointed...)
Manaka
Thank you for walking me home... You're so kind.
It's really late now.
Hehe, see you.
Ah, bye.
It's really hot tonight...
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry for the wait.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. You look good in a yukata.
Hehe, thanks.
Then shall we go to the Bay Bridge？
Manaka
Ah, the fireworks just now...
They're heart-shaped.
Hmm？
Nothing. I wonder if they will shoot some more...
Manaka
The fireworks are beautiful...
Are you listening？ What？ What are you staring at？
▲高嶺＊＊▲ watching the fireworks is just so beautiful.
...Hey.
Um, at times like this, I feel like we don't have to say a word to understand each other... I'm happy.
But I want to talk about fireworks with you later, so you have to watch properly, okay？
You mean watching ▲高嶺＊＊▲ or the fireworks？
Manaka
Thank you for walking me home... You're so kind.
It's really late now.
Hehe, see you.
Ah, bye.
(Okay, the new semester starts today！)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what's up？
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
...This is great. Now we can meet at school everyday...
Hmm？ What？
Nothing！ Let's enjoy the new semester.
(Well, today is the school's closing ceremony！)
Ah, after this, we'll have a long school break！
Manaka
You seem happy.
Well, aren't you happy, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Not really. If it's the school break...
Hmm？ What？
...Never mind. I just wish that the break would end soon...
(But it hasn't even started yet...)
(I think the exam results have been announced...)
(I did perfectly for the exams this time.)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. You did a great job.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. You, too.
Your grades are really great！ Now we're such worthy rivals, right？
If you say so, I'll have to work even harder.
Hehe, I won't lose to you... Let's try our best.
(All right. I'll study hard！)
(I think the exam results have been announced...)
(The result isn't bad, but isn't good either... Quite mediocre...)
Manaka
Just try a bit harder, okay？
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
If it's you, I know you can do better than this if you try.
...I want our names to be close together on the ranking board, so please study harder, okay？
(All right. Next time, I should study harder.)
(I think the exam results have been announced...)
(I got really bad result from the exams this time...)
Manaka
...Hey, if you have anything you don't understand, you can ask me anytime, okay？
I can't do anything much, but at least I can help answering your questions. I want to help you. So, please.
Okay, thanks.
(I made her worried... Ah, I really have to study harder. Really...！)
(We have a tennis tournament today.)
(Hah... I'm nervous.)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. Are you nervous？
▲高嶺＊＊▲... Y-Yeah, just a little bit. No, I think I just can't wait for the match to start.
Hehe, calm down. I'll give you this good luck charm. It's very effective, so you can rest assured. Now, close your eyes.
Close my eyes？ O-Okay.
Don't peek, okay？
(...Hmm？ Something soft is touching my forehead...)
...How do you feel now？
Eh？ Ah, I feel the best...
Hehe, that's great. Put all your effort in the match, okay？ I'll put all my effort cheering for you, too.
I'll see you later, all right？
(Whatever she did to me, now the tension has been gone！ All right！ I've got to give it my all！)
(All right, perfect！)
Manaka
Congratulations！ That was great work！
Thanks, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, I owe it to your support.
...When you say that, it makes me happy. But I think you really are talented.
You played so well that I couldn't take my eyes off of you... Now, you should take a rest, okay？
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ looks so happy. I'm glad I won.)
(This is no good...)
Manaka
How unfortunate...
Sorry, even though you were cheering for me.
No, don't worry. I thought it was a nice match...
But I know you're probably disappointed. Just take a break for today, okay？
Yeah... Thanks. I'll rest a bit.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ I really wanted to win for you, but...)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you need something？
...Can't I call my boyfriend when I have a birthday present for him？
I see. Yeah, today is my birthday. Thank you！
Hehe... Geez, look at you. At least, don't forget my birthday, okay？
And here's your present. Will you take it？
Of course！ Thanks.
You're welcome. If you don't want it, just give it back to me any time.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, do you think I could give away a gift from you？ Even if the world turned upside-down, that wouldn't happen.
Geez, why do you always say such cheesy things.
Hehe, anyway, I'm glad that you're happy. Happy birthday.
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What's up？
Um, today is your birthday, right？ So, here you go...
A present！？ Thank you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
You're welcome. If you don't like it, please say so. You can just return it then.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, how can I not like a present from you？
Is it okay to say that when you haven't even seen it？
It's okay！
Hehe, just hearing you say that makes me happy.
Okay, happy birthday. I wish you a wonderful year ahead.
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What's up？
